Installation
as Dockerhost we use Debian in a VM. This VM runs on my Proxmox Node.

The Installation is straight forward and can be read [here](../01%20-%20Work%20environment.md)






Bash Script

#!/bin/bash
# Stop running container
docker-compose -f /path/to/docker-compose.yml down

# Pull new Image
docker-compose -f /path/to/docker-compose.yml pull

# Start container
docker-compose -f /path/to/docker-compose.yml up -d